PREAMBLE

This license governs the use, modification, distribution, and commercial
application of the BUGRAIDER Deep Code Audit Prompt and any derivative works
based upon it (collectively referred to as "the Software").

BUGRAIDER is a text-based prompt designed to instruct AI language models.
It is NOT a software application, NOT a service, and NOT a tool with guaranteed
output. nRn World provides this prompt as a free resource and makes no
representations or guarantees of any kind regarding its performance,
accuracy, safety, or fitness for any particular purpose.

